text: I absolutely love my bracelet! It's so pretty and fantastic quality for the price. The packaging makes you feel so special when you receive it. Beautifully packaged and the dried rose petals are such a special touch. Simply stunning. It was delivered in a matter of days after placing the order, very fast and efficient.
